# Knowledge vault data — the vault is its OWN git repo (git is its audit log),
# so this outer repo must never track it (otherwise it lands as an embedded-repo
# gitlink). Ignores the skill's default in-tree location; if you set
# KNOWLEDGE_VAULT elsewhere, keep the vault outside this tree instead.
/vault/

